Key Match Events: Shadab Khan's all-round excellence helped Pakistan to 185 for nine.
Shadab Khan hit 52 from just 22 deliveries, contributing four sixes.
Shaheen Shah Afridi took three wickets for 14 runs.
South Africa's target was reduced to 142 from 14 overs due to rain.
South Africa ended with 108 for nine.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was rain-affected and played under the Duckworth-Lewis-Stern method.
